  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help rebuild the homes lost in the fire in Athens</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">On Monday, July 23rd, multiple fires erupted near Mati and Rafina, seaside areas of Athens, Greece. Fanned by winds of up to 60 miles per hour, the fires quickly grew into raging infernos claiming the lives of over 90 people, completely destroying over 1,200 homes and leaving a whole country in a state of shock.   This project aims to humbly help families rebuild their homes.</narrative>
  </description>
